query_results.description: Find all people who have credit cards with CVV code 778
query_results.query: SELECT p.full_name, p.person_id, cc.card_no FROM people p JOIN credit_cards cc ON p.person_id = cc.owner_id WHERE cc.cvv = '778'

query_results.description: Check how many pets each person with CVV 778 owns
query_results.query: SELECT p.full_name, p.person_id, COUNT(pt.pet_id) as pet_count FROM people p JOIN credit_cards cc ON p.person_id = cc.owner_id LEFT JOIN pets pt ON p.person_id = pt.owner_id WHERE cc.cvv = '778' GROUP BY p.person_id, p.full_name

query_results.description: Find the bank accounts for the person with zero pets among CVV 778 holders
query_results.query: SELECT ba.account_no, ba.balance FROM bank_accounts ba WHERE ba.owner_id = (SELECT p.person_id FROM people p JOIN credit_cards cc ON p.person_id = cc.owner_id LEFT JOIN pets pt ON p.person_id = pt.owner_id WHERE cc.cvv = '778' GROUP BY p.person_id HAVING COUNT(pt.pet_id) = 0) ORDER BY ba.balance DESC
